c: 3
v: 55
t: "Jjukira ekiseera Katonda bweyagamba nti; Owange ggwe Isa nze ngenda kukutuukiririza ekyo kyenakuwandiikako, era ngenda kusitula nkuleete gyendi era nkutukuze kwabo abaakaafuwala, abo abakugoberera ngenda kubassa waggulu waabo abakafuwala okutuusa ku lunaku lw’enkomerero oluvanyuma gyendi mwenna gyemugenda okudda, olwo ndyoke mbalamule mwebyo byemwayawukanangamu"